snippet.title: The Other Sprinter - Dismantling the Donor to Save my Van.
snippet.description:
I take the plunge into dismantling this very rusty Ex-gritting Mercedes Sprinter in order to save my home on wheels.
Despite the doubts and mammoth task ahead, with plenty of research and labelling of parts & wirings, I start to make headway.

Project Amber Merch:
https://projectamber.creator-spring.com

Find most parts, items & accesories I've used in videos on my
Amazon Store:
https://www.amazon.co.uk/shop/projectamber
You can also follow on:
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/project.amber/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ProjectAmber25.Vanlife/
